sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-In Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over HF,S3: Initialization (HuggingFace Detector)
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        S3->>HF: KServe Storage Initializer<br/>downloads model files<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
        Note over HF: Model loaded into<br/>GPU/CPU memory
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-In Text Content Detection
    rect rgb(213, 232, 212)
        Orchestrator->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP plaintext (intra-mesh)<br/>Auth: None
        Note over BuiltIn: Regex PII matching<br/>+ File-type validation<br/>(in-process)
        BuiltIn-->>Orchestrator: Detection results<br/>(ContentAnalysisResponse)
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace ML Model Detection
    rect rgb(218, 232, 252)
        Orchestrator->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP + Istio mTLS<br/>Auth: detector_id header
        Note over HF: PyTorch inference<br/>AutoModelForSequenceClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM<br/>(in-process, GPU/CPU)
        HF-->>Orchestrator: Detection results<br/>HTTP + Istio mTLS
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    rect rgb(255, 242, 204)
        Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP + Istio mTLS<br/>Auth: detector_id header
        Judge->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext (intra-mesh)<br/>Auth: None
        vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation result
        Judge-->>Orchestrator: Detection results<br/>HTTP + Istio mTLS
    end

    Note over Orchestrator,vLLM: Flow 3b: LLM Judge Generation Evaluation
    rect rgb(255, 242, 204)
        Orchestrator->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>HTTP + Istio mTLS<br/>Auth: detector_id header
        Judge->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext (intra-mesh)<br/>Auth: None
        vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation result
        Judge-->>Orchestrator: Generation evaluation results<br/>HTTP + Istio mTLS
    end
